Package edu.american

Interface Summary
Painter Painter for all graphics.
 

Class Summary
Dots Creates the dots.
EndGame Constructs the end of game window which allows the user to play again or quit.
GameFrame The game play window on which the background, player, and npcs are drawn.
Main Constructs everything and updates all players and NPCs.
Menu The menu which allows the user to pick their players.
NPC Creates the NPC players and checks their status.
Player Creates player (sprite) and updates their location.
ScorePainter Paints the score on the game frame and adds points.
